```

### Common Tasks
```bash
# Clear all caches
ddev ee cache:clear

# Sync templates to database
ddev ee sync:template

# List installed add-ons
ddev ee addons:list

# Install an add-on
ddev ee addons:install addon_name
```

## Template Patterns

### Channel Entries
```html
{exp:channel:entries channel="pages" url_title="{segment_2}"}
    <h1>{title}</h1>
    {body}
{/exp:channel:entries}
```

### Stash Caching
```html
{exp:stash:set name="page_content" save="yes" scope="site" replace="no"}
    {exp:channel:entries channel="news" limit="10"}
        <article>{title}</article>
    {/exp:channel:entries}
{/exp:stash:set}

{exp:stash:get name="page_content"}
```

### Embeds/Partials
```html
{embed="_partials/_header"}
{embed="_partials/_footer"}
```

### Layouts (EE Layout system)
```html
{!-- In layout template --}
{layout:set name="page_title"}{title}{/layout:set}

{!-- In child template --}
{layout="layouts/_main"}
```

